People Hold On...The Remix Anthology is a remix album by British singer Lisa
Stansfield, released by Edsel Records on 10 November 2014. It contains remixes
of songs originally included on Stansfield's albums released between 1989 and 2001
The tracks were remixed by various prominent producers. In Europe, the album was
issued on 21 November 2014.
